 degree adjustable,you can easily adjust your cellphone to most comfortable viewing angle</div><div>【 24 Hours Customer Service 】Any question about SHAWE cell phone stand, please contact us via E-mail at first. We have an 18 months replacement service and professional customer service support.</div></div>', 'Shawe Phone holder main.png', TIMESTAMP '2020-09-30 17:21:46.000000', TIMESTAMP '2020-09-30 17:21:46.000000', 1, 1, 15.65, 18.99, 0, 2.2, 2.2, 1.2, 0.3, 35, 19, 0, 0);
