ing the latest version of Bluetooth wireless communication: Bluetooth 5. 0. When paired with Bluetooth 5. 0 peripherals, this system can deliver improved performance, more wireless range and higher data transfer rates, while also providing enough bandwidth to support two devices.</div><div>System Ram Type: Ddr4 Sdram</div></div>', 'Dell Inspiron 27 AIO main.png', TIMESTAMP '2020-10-01 10:55:42.000000', TIMESTAMP '2020-11-13 09:49:15.000000', 1, 1, 1550, 1639, 0, 16, 12, 2, 24.5, 38, 5, 0, 0);
