er TX3000E</div></div>', 'TPLink AX3000 main.png', TIMESTAMP '2020-10-04 13:59:58.000000', TIMESTAMP '2020-10-04 13:59:58.000000', 1, 1, 38, 49.99, 0, 5, 4, 2, 1, 54, 31, 4, 1);
